SAINT B ERNARD
PROFESSIONAL HUMAN TRAINER"
Will train any
human to perform
the following basic
obedience commands:
1. Fetch me a treat
2. Rub my belly
3. Pick up my poop
4. Wipe my feet
5. Speak baby talk
6. Throw the ball
7. Don't hog the bed
8. Give me a kiss
9. Buy me a toy
10. Fetch me a treat
(this one's good!)
